title: Brady wins Deflategate & AFC preview
itunes:title: Brady wins Deflategate & AFC preview
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – discuss the impact Tom Brady's return will have on the Patriots and the NFL going forward. The guys then preview the AFC team by team and predict the playoff picture.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
